<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />

  <title>FlowCRM | Calculadora de ROI para Automação de Marketing</title>

  <style>
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    html {
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: "Inter", "Manrope", Arial, sans-serif;
      background: #ffffff;
      color: #191923;
    }

    img {
      max-width: 100%;
      display: block;
    }

    a {
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    /* =========================
       HERO
    ========================= */

    .hero-section {
      width: 100%;
      min-height: 100vh;
      padding: 32px 24px 96px;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(255, 79, 139, 0.16), transparent 34%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 80% 65%, rgba(255, 122, 48, 0.14), transparent 32%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #fff7f3 0%, #ffffff 100%);
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .hero-nav {
      max-width: 1180px;
      margin: 0 auto 72px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }

    .logo {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 10px;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: #191923;
    }

    .logo-mark {
      width: 34px;
      height: 34px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff4f8b, #ff7a30);
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      color: #ffffff;
      font-weight: 900;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .nav-link {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #ff4f8b;
    }

    .hero-container {
      max-width: 1180px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 0.95fr 1.05fr;
      gap: 64px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .hero-copy {
      max-width: 620px;
    }

    .hero-badge {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 10px 16px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: #ffffff;
      box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(25, 25, 35, 0.08);
      color: #ff4f8b;
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .hero-copy h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 6vw, 5.4rem);
      line-height: 0.95;
      letter-spacing: -0.07em;
      color: #191923;
    }

    .hero-copy p {
      margin: 28px 0 0;
      max-width: 560px;
      font-size: 1.16rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: #4b4b5c;
    }

    .hero-actions {
      margin-top: 36px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .primary-button {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 17px 28px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff4f8b, #ff7a30);
      color: #ffffff;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      box-shadow: 0 18px 36px rgba(255, 79, 139, 0.28);
      transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
    }

    .primary-button:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 22px 42px rgba(255, 79, 139, 0.34);
    }

    .hero-microcopy {
      font-size: 0.92rem;
      color: #6b6b7a;
    }

    .hero-bullets {
      margin: 32px 0 0;
      padding: 0;
      list-style: none;
      display: grid;
      gap: 13px;
      color: #30303d;
      font-size: 0.98rem;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .hero-bullets li {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .hero-bullets li::before {
      content: "✓";
      flex: 0 0 auto;
      width: 22px;
      height: 22px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: #fff1f6;
      color: #ff4f8b;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      font-weight: 900;
    }

    .hero-visual {
      position: relative;
    }

    .hero-visual::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 8% 0 auto 8%;
      width: 86%;
      height: 86%;
      border-radius: 44px;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 79, 139, 0.18), rgba(255, 122, 48, 0.14));
      filter: blur(10px);
      z-index: 0;
    }

    .mockup-frame {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
      padding: 14px;
      border-radius: 34px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72);
      box-shadow: 0 28px 70px rgba(25, 25, 35, 0.16);
      backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
    }

    .mockup-frame img {
      width: 100%;
      border-radius: 24px;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(25, 25, 35, 0.10);
    }

    /* =========================
       CONTEXTO
    ========================= */

    .context-section {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 96px 24px;
      background: #fffaf7;
    }

    .context-container {
      max-width: 1180px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 72px;
      align-items: start;
    }

    .section-label {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
      font-size: 0.82rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: #ff4f8b;
    }

    .context-title h2 {
      margin: 0;
      max-width: 520px;
      font-size: clamp(2.3rem, 4vw, 4.3rem);
      line-height: 1.02;
      letter-spacing: -0.06em;
      color: #191923;
    }

    .context-copy {
      max-width: 580px;
      padding-top: 44px;
    }

    .context-copy p {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 1.08rem;
      line-height: 1.75;
      color: #4b4b5c;
    }

    .context-copy p + p {
      margin-top: 28px;
    }

    /* =========================
       RESPONSIVO
    ========================= */

    @media (max-width: 980px) {
      .hero-section {
        min-height: auto;
        padding-bottom: 72px;
      }

      .hero-nav {
        margin-bottom: 52px;
      }

      .hero-container {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 56px;
      }

      .hero-copy {
        max-width: 760px;
      }

      .hero-copy h1 {
        max-width: 760px;
      }

      .hero-copy p {
        max-width: 680px;
      }

      .hero-visual {
        max-width: 760px;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }

      .context-container {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 32px;
      }

      .context-copy {
        max-width: 100%;
        padding-top: 0;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .hero-section {
        padding: 24px 20px 64px;
      }

      .hero-nav {
        margin-bottom: 48px;
      }

      .nav-link {
        display: none;
      }

      .hero-copy h1 {
        font-size: clamp(2.55rem, 14vw, 4rem);
      }

      .hero-copy p {
        font-size: 1.03rem;
        line-height: 1.65;
      }

      .primary-button {
        width: 100%;
        padding: 16px 22px;
      }

      .hero-actions {
        width: 100%;
      }

      .mockup-frame {
        padding: 9px;
        border-radius: 24px;
      }

      .mockup-frame img {
        border-radius: 18px;
      }

      .context-section {
        padding: 72px 20px;
      }

      .context-title h2 {
        max-width: 100%;
        font-size: clamp(2.1rem, 10vw, 3.2rem);
      }

      .context-copy p {
        font-size: 1rem;
        line-height: 1.7;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <section class="hero-section">
    <nav class="hero-nav">
      <a href="#" class="logo" aria-label="FlowCRM">
        <span class="logo-mark">F</span>
        <span>FlowCRM</span>
      </a>

      <a href="#calculator" class="nav-link">Acessar calculadora</a>
    </nav>

    <div class="hero-container">
      <div class="hero-copy">
        <span class="hero-badge">Calculadora gratuita</span>

        <h1>Calcule o ROI da automação de marketing em menos de 2 minutos</h1>

        <p>
          Descubra quanto tempo sua equipe pode economizar ao automatizar tarefas
          manuais, melhorar fluxos de campanha e reduzir esforço operacional.
        </p>

        <div class="hero-actions">
          <a href="#calculator" class="primary-button">Ver minha estimativa de economia</a>
          <span class="hero-microcopy">
            Calculadora gratuita. Resultado estimado com base na rotina atual da sua equipe.
          </span>
        </div>

        <ul class="hero-bullets">
          <li>Estime ganhos de produtividade</li>
          <li>Identifique tarefas que podem ser automatizadas</li>
          <li>Visualize economia de tempo e recursos</li>
          <li>Receba recomendações para otimizar sua operação</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="hero-visual">
        <div class="mockup-frame">
          <img src="assets/mockup-flowcrm.png" alt="Mockup da calculadora de ROI da FlowCRM">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="context-section">
    <div class="context-container">
      <div class="context-title">
        <span class="section-label">O desafio</span>
        <h2>Quanto tempo sua equipe ainda perde com tarefas manuais?</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="context-copy">
        <p>
          Campanhas, listas, aprovações, relatórios, follow-ups e ajustes operacionais
          fazem parte da rotina de marketing. O problema começa quando essas tarefas
          passam a consumir tempo demais e reduzem o espaço para análise, planejamento
          e melhoria contínua.
        </p>

        <p>
          Com processos mais bem estruturados e automações nos pontos certos, a equipe
          reduz retrabalho, ganha previsibilidade e mantém as campanhas rodando com
          mais consistência.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</body>
</html>
